lead_paragraph: Gut, of Switzerland, overtook the injured Lindsey Vonn by finishing fourth in the next-to-last giant slalom of the season, won by Eva-Maria Brem.

headline.print_headline: Brem Wins World Cup GS, Gut Goes Top of Overall Standings
headline.main: Lara Gut Moves to Top of Overall World Cup Standings
